#

Thai Pork Coconut Curry

$15.99
620 kcal

Allergens:

Fish Sauce

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

ThaiCurryPork

Description

A fragrant and creamy Thai curry featuring tender pork and fresh vegetables, served with jasmine rice for a delightful experience.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 1 lb
  • Coconut milk: 1 can (14 oz)
  • Red curry paste: 3 tbsp
  • Fish sauce: 2 tbsp
  • Brown sugar: 1 tbsp
  • Bell pepper: 1, sliced
  • Carrot: 1, sliced
  • Basil leaves: 1/2 cup
  • Jasmine rice: 1 cup
  • Water: 2 cups
